HEADWORD: Tractation
<hw>Trac*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tractatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>Treatment or handling of a subject;
discussion.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A full <qex>tractation</qex> of the points controverted.</q>
